![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fdd17abe-2df6-40b0-a217-e1a50164779b/Ep208.jpg)

Happy Belated Birthday Wade Wilson! Our resident 'Merc with a Mouth' known to most as Deadpool, has shocked us on both the page and the silver screen, having captivated audiences and readers alike with his meta humor and gratuitous violence for 30 years. Some would argue his biggest feat was his destruction of the Marvel Universe, so what a great way to celebrate the chimichanga enthusiast than to review that very 4-issue story here on the podcast! Check it out!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

  
